<title>bḥwr ạlgẖrbẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- wsṭ bḥwr ạltyh wạlgẖrbẗ wzmạn mlyạn bạlạ̉ḥzạn
 ạ̉yạm mrẗ wạ̉yạm ṣʿbẗ wạlfrḥ mạlwsẖ fyhạ mkạn
 1- ḍạqt by yạrb ḥyạty wạldnyạ ktyr btlṭmny
 bạrfʿ lyk yạ ạ̹lhy ṣlạty mn jrḥy wạ̉ḥzạny ạrḥmny
 2- dnyạ wkl mạ fyhạ tjạrb tzrʿ jwh qlwbnạ jrạḥ
 ʿạysẖyn fyhạ snyn bnḥạrb msẖ ʿạrfyn ạmty̱ hạnrtạḥ
 3- ʿạlm bqy̱ mn ṭbʿh ạlqswẗ ḥty̱ ʿynynạ mlạhạ dmwʿ
 kl snyn ạlʿmry mạ tswy̱ lḥẓẗ wqrb ạ̹lhnạ yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>